Could size be dynamic?

For example, blooming to an enlarged "attention-getting" size while slewing
or moving rapidly, shrinking to a "precision" size (pointer, I-beam, fist,
or whatever is appropriate to hovering context)...provided that kind of
behavior isn't blocked by some patently obvious patent ;-)

